<section class="section">
  <h2>🌍 Our Tour Packages | எங்கள் சுற்றுலா தொகுப்புகள்</h2>
  <h3>7-Day Itinerary: Chennai → Madurai → Rameswaram → Kanyakumari</h3>

  <div class="itinerary">
    <h4>Day 1: Arrival in Chennai</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Arrival</strong>: Reach Chennai and check-in.</li>
      <li><strong>Sightseeing</strong>: Visit Marina Beach, Kapaleeshwarar Temple.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="itinerary">
    <h4>Day 2: Chennai → Madurai</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Departure</strong>: Drive to Madurai.</li>
      <li><strong>Sightseeing</strong>: Meenakshi Amman Temple, Thirumalai Nayakkar Mahal.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="itinerary">
    <h4>Day 3: Madurai → Rameswaram</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Departure</strong>: Drive to Rameswaram.</li>
      <li><strong>Sightseeing</strong>: Ramanathaswamy Temple, Pamban Bridge, Dhanushkodi Beach.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="itinerary">
    <h4>Day 4: Rameswaram → Kanyakumari</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Departure</strong>: Drive to Kanyakumari.</li>
      <li><strong>Sightseeing</strong>: Vivekananda Rock Memorial, Thiruvalluvar Statue.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="itinerary">
    <h4>Day 5: Kanyakumari Full Day</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Morning</strong>: Watch sunrise at Vivekananda Rock Memorial.</li>
      <li><strong>Sightseeing</strong>: Kanyakumari Temple, Sunset Point.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="itinerary">
    <h4>Day 6: Kanyakumari → Madurai</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Return</strong>: Drive back to Madurai.</li>
      <li><strong>Sightseeing</strong>: Optional visit to Sri Meenakshi Temple.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="itinerary">
    <h4>Day 7: Madurai → Chennai</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Return</strong>: Drive back to Chennai for departure.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

